                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6750" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0324</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8219 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百年蚌压梦 变革创辉煌：蚌埠压缩机的组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A century-old dream of mussel compression, change to create brilliance: organizational change of Bengbu compressor</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋宁，苏家平，张薇薇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安瑞科（蚌埠）压缩机有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革；组织变革方向；蚌埠压缩机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">organizational change; direction of organizational change; Bengbu compressor</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蚌埠压缩机是蚌埠市的第一家机械制造企业，更是安徽省第一家国营企业。历经七十多年发展，一路坎坷。2017年更是蚌埠压缩机的一个转折点，面对新能源的崛起、市场竞争的冲击，三年时间的组织变革让其从濒临破产到重现辉煌。案例描述了蚌埠压缩机坚决突破旧思想、打破旧体制，挣脱一切不利于企业发展的束缚（解冻），以创新新业务模式、优化组织机构、变革考核分配制度以及激活人力资源为主的深化变革（变革），建立管理学院，让变革“深入灵魂，触及骨髓”（再冻结）的组织变革过程。而变革之后，在互联网背景下作为传统制造企业的蚌埠压缩机为实现“百年蚌压梦”，将面临新的挑战，新变革之路的方向悬而未决。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Bengbu Compressor is the first machinery manufacturing enterprise in Bengbu City and the first state-owned enterprise in Anhui Province. After more than 70 years of development, the road has been bumpy. 2017 was a turning point for Bengbu Compressor. In the face of the rise of new energy sources and the impact of market competition, three years of organizational reform made it from the brink of bankruptcy to a resurgence. The case describes that Bengbu Compressor resolutely broke through the old ideas, broke the old system, got rid of all the constraints (unfreeze) that are not conducive to the development of the enterprise, and deepened the reform by innovating new business models, optimizing organizational structures, changing the assessment and distribution system, and activating human resources. (change), establish a management school, and let the change &quot;go deep into the soul and touch the marrow&quot; (refreeze) the organizational change process. After the change, Bengbu Compressor, as a traditional manufacturing enterprise under the background of the Internet, will face new challenges in order to realize the &quot;hundred-year-old Beng Ya’ dream&quot;, and the direction of the new road of change is still pending.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织变革驱动力；组织变革方向；组织变革内容；组织变革阻力；组织变革阻力克服；组织变革过程</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
